### Test Order Creation API

### 1. Order WITHOUT Account (Guest)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeId": "f6088716-ca5e-4ed0-bef4-3dfe3abb51b8",
  "type": "DELIVERY",
  "customerInfo": {
    "name": "John Guest",
    "phone": "0901234567"
  },
  "note": "Guest order - no account",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "983d1ab2-1a87-4425-9352-3c410ed0c537",
      "quantity": 2,
      "note": "Less ice"
    },
    {
      "productId": "f96eb57d-4044-4a4a-99fa-44efca636b7f",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

